<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SPORTMATCH — 로그인 필요</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;0,9..40,700;1,9..40,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>
<div class="error-page">
  <div class="error-bg-number">401</div>

  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center">
    <div class="error-emoji">🔐</div>
    <div class="error-code">401 · Unauthorized</div>
    <div class="error-title">로그인이 필요해요</div>
    <div class="error-desc">
      이 페이지는 로그인한 회원만 이용할 수 있어요.<br>
      SPORTMATCH에 로그인하고 매칭에 참가해 보세요!
    </div>
    <div class="error-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-accent btn-lg" onclick="location.href='/login'">🚀 로그인하기</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="location.href='/register'">회원가입</button>
    </div>

    <div class="login-card">
      <div class="login-card-title">🏃 바로 로그인</div>
      <input class="login-input" type="text" placeholder="이메일 또는 아이디" />
      <input class="login-input" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호" />
      <button class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%" onclick="location.href='/login'">로그인 →</button>
      <div style="margin-top:12px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);text-align:center">
        계정이 없으신가요? <a href="/register" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">회원가입</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
